(72769, '694F72D9-41C7-4D3C-882C-CDB39E1D14A1', 'We agree to see partners no more frequently than 1x per month and will discuss with each other prior to committing to any plans. We agree to limit communication to every 3days (72hrs), plus required communications for essential logistics/planning. We will set expectations for our return time and agree to 11pm unless discussed/agreed upon in advance (I.e. for special events/concerts, etc.)  We will check in with one another prior to starting a date, and if we do sleep with another partner, to shower before coming to bed.', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2023-10-23T08:43:01.879827'),
(72770, '39672EA0-0559-4E74-BCD3-5D714A97F20D', 'I am sorry that I broke our agreement by coming home late, when I set the expectation that I would home by 11, per our agreement. I know this hurt you not only because it deprived us of the time to reconnect, but added to your frustration caused by me breaking our communications agreement with Amanda. I understand that we’ve created these agreements for both of us to feel secure as well as to help our partners know in advance how we can engage, so they feel considered and are able to decide whether or not to invest their time/energy.  I was not as vigilant as I should have been on tracking the time last night and didn’t consider the impact this would have on you (and us). I feel really ashamed for missing the mark here and not reciprocating, as I know you  have worked hard to be home on time and communicating to me your plans, and sticking to them. ', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2023-10-23T09:58:59.981222'),
